        public DefaultClientResources.Builder eventLoopGroupProvider(EventLoopGroupProvider eventLoopGroupProvider)

The provided EventLoopGroupProvider instance will not be shut down when shutting down the client resources. You have to take care of that. This is an advanced configuration that should only be used if you know what you are doing.
